The switch is in an odd location, above and behind the driver, just
behind the roof light.  There's a chrome handle that says "Golde" on it.
 Turn it clockwise 90 degrees and slide backwards.  "On" is easy enough.
 "Off" can be a real bear at 55mph! :)

